channel.title: I need help from all of you!
channel.description: hello all I'm making a trouble shorter for RSPS's and i need problems! and how to resolve them. Once complete the trouble shorter will help thouthands of people with the little things to the fatal errors. you will be included in the credits. i'm still working on the main things but and don't have time to find and create problems and then figer them out. so please post some detailed problems that you have personaly expirienced and how you resolved them, would be a great help to me. :) will be released soon
